headline: Cocoa Prices Tumble on West African Cocoa Crop Optimism
summary: December ICE NY cocoa (CCZ25 ) on Thursday closed down -270 (-3.52%), and December ICE London cocoa #7 (CAZ25 ) closed down -126 (-2.39%). Cocoa prices fell sharply on Thursday, with London cocoa posting a 6-week low, after chocolate maker Mondelez International expressed optimism about this year's cocoa crop harvest...

headline: How Is Mondelez’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Consumer Staples Stocks?
summary: While Mondelez’s performance has been weak compared to its consumer staples peers, Wall Street remains optimistic about its prospects.
